00:01:01.220 --> 00:01:03.490
of years, unless it's your birthday today, in which case,

00:01:03.490 --> 00:01:06.140
happy birthday. But otherwise, you'd need to add the number

00:01:06.140 --> 00:01:09.330
of days since your birthday to get a more accurate

00:01:09.330 --> 00:01:14.210
number. I'll change my age to my real age. And

00:01:14.210 --> 00:01:16.750
I will add the number of days since my birthday.

